The Vanilla-DMZ cursor theme is a style neutral scalable cursor theme.

This package include both themes, white and black. If you want one, ie
black theme, run the script as follow: THEME=Vanilla-DMZ-AA ./vanilla-dmz.SlackBuild

For using white theme put

    Xcursor.theme:    Vanilla-DMZ
    
or for using black theme put

    Xcursor.theme:    Vanilla-DMZ-AA

in your XResources file.
